service: booking-app-backend

provider:
  name: aws
  runtime: nodejs18.x
  region: ap-south-1
  stage: ${opt:stage, 'dev'} # Default to 'dev' if not provided
  environment:
    BOOKINGS_TABLE: ${self:provider.stage}-bookings-table

functions:
  getBookings:
    handler: handlers/getBookings.handler
    events:
      - http:
          path: bookings
          method: get

  createBooking:
    createBooking:
    handler: handler.createBooking
    events:
      - http:
          path: bookings
          method: post
